scripture:2 corinthians 13:14:: The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ, and the love of God, and the fellowship of the Holy Spirit, be with us all evermore.
scripture:romans 15:13:: May the God of hope fill us with all joy and peace in believing through the power of the Holy Spirit.
scripture:ephesians 3:20-21:: Glory to God whose power, working in us, can do infinitely more than we can ask or imagine: Glory to him from generation to generation in the Church, and in Christ Jesus for ever and ever.

